pBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/pcsx2-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizei148.84 MBdbsumx@6ac501d055b7b16b592fd3a3cd76ea89d2203dfdfe96f466aa18f4fa4ec2d960jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkgvpolybar.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namegPolybarfpkg_idx8github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.polybar-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxuhttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/polybar-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.16 MBdbsumx@248c4aaa06106b934e9f1bc013e9c67377a46fed88ba9fb4b86258eccd91eab3jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCęcpkgvquake3e.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namepQuake3e (engine)fpkg_idx8github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.quake3e-29_05_2025-xplshnkdescriptionwQuake 3 Enhanced enginepdescription_longyÚThis is a modern Quake III Arena engine aimed to be fast, secure and compatible with all existing Q3A mods. It is based on last non-SDL source dump of ioquake3 with latest upstream fixes applied.

Key features:

* Optimized OpenGL renderer
* Optimized Vulkan renderer
* Raw mouse input support, enabled automatically instead of DirectInput(\in_mouse 1) if available
* Unlagged mouse events processing, can be reverted by setting \in_lagged 1
* \in_minimize - hotkey for minimize/restore main window (win32-only, direct replacement for Q3Minimizer)
* \video-pipe - to use external ffmpeg binary as an encoder for better quality and smaller output files
* Significantly reworked QVM (Quake Virtual Machine)
* Improved server-side DoS protection, much reduced memory usage
* Raised filesystem limits (up to 20,000 maps can be handled in a single directory)
* Reworked Zone memory allocator, no more out-of-memory errors
* Non-intrusive support for SDL2 backend (video, audio, input), selectable at compile time
* Tons of bug fixes and other improvements
* Vulkan renderer based on Quake-III-Arena-Kenny-Edition with many additions:

* High-quality per-pixel dynamic lighting
* Very fast flares (\r_flares 1)
* Anisotropic filtering (\r_ext_texture_filter_anisotropic)
* Greatly reduced API overhead (call/dispatch ratio)
* Flexible vertex buffer memory management to allow loading huge maps
* Multiple command buffers to reduce processing bottlenecks
* Reversed depth buffer to eliminate z-fighting on big maps
* Merged lightmaps (atlases)
* Multitexturing optimizations
* Static world surfaces cached in VBO (\r_vbo 1)
* Useful debug markers for tools like RenderDoc
* Fixed framebuffer corruption on some Intel iGPUs
* Offscreen rendering, enabled with \r_fbo 1, all following requires it enabled:

* ScreenMap texture rendering - to create realistic environment reflections
* Multisample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_multisample)
* Supersample anti-aliasing (\r_ext_supersample)
* Per-window gamma-correction which is important for screen-capture tools like OBS
* You can minimize game window any time during \video|\video-pipe recording
* High dynamic range render targets (\r_hdr 1) to avoid color banding
* Bloom post-processing effect
* Arbitrary resolution rendering
* Greyscale modeldownload_urlxchttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/quake3e.dwfs.AppBundledsizeg8.36 MBdbsumx@e7a5f8b95ba104774f719eeb60f581e1936d0d5c4bf8d92cb78c67fabada2247jbuild_datex2025-05-29 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkguscrcpy.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefScrcpyfpkg_idx7github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.scrcpy-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/scrcpy-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh39.53 MBdbsumx@4cdc7acf22921c22b231e9eff8ec9b8c325c179969680ef2523fdf46fe1d2a5cjbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkguthunar.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namefThunarfpkg_idx7github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.thunar-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxthttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/thunar-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.42 MBdbsumx@c5d3b40af1c3d9cc4a5ed5bc2e694eede18b0453d9d43eae5411e5bb3cfcdbcfjbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkgxxfce4-multicall.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_nameoXfce4 Multicallfpkg_idx@github.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-multicall-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlx}https://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/xfce4-multicall-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh18.22 MBdbsumx@b14f17a2e6f076b5e4c1ebec763440765e4fcd0da9974ce9478213ed85378122jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkgx"xfce4-power-manager.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namesXfce4 Power Managerfpkg_idxDgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-power-manager-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxühttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBundleHUB/releases/download/v121-20250626143406/xfce4-power-manager-26_06_2025-xplshn.dwfs.AppBundledsizeh12.16 MBdbsumx@ea2e8e182e5ec2cf8ccc123c6f7f7a393428b9e5a6b0f6d6394efcca0d4299d9jbuild_datex2025-06-26 00:00:00 +0000 UTCžcpkgx"xfce4-screenshooter.dwfs.AppBundlehpkg_namesXfce4 Screenshooterfpkg_idxDgithub.com.xplshn.appbundlehub.xfce4-screenshooter-26_06_2025-xplshnldownload_urlxühttps://github.com/xplshn/AppBun